*.parquet

# ── Intermediate / legacy analysis (superseded by results/) ─────────────────
submission_artifacts_en/
legacy/
mdpi_mathematics_submission_package/

# ── Manuscript (added to GitHub after journal acceptance) ───────────────────
paper/

